你都知道邊個係施永清<br />\n佢啱啱開始發蹟嗰陣 <br />\n有幾個風水佬同佢講做地產最緊要信風水 <br />\n跟住佢就問返啲風水佬，我唔信風水，你要我信嘅話 <br />\n咁你話畀我聽，我究竟擺啲乜係屋企可以令我即刻死，跟住啲風水佬呆撚曬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d21af2b57c137d8fee68fdbca939a33173b47f9","tid":1746382,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"你淨係睇連登有條友連8字都計錯<br />\n之後要求del post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就知好撚多神棍"},{"pid":"a51558a1edfdb87dbc895dec1a46fadce04c899e","tid":1746382,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d21af2b57c137d8fee68fdbca939a33173b47f9","tid":1746382,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"你淨係睇連登有條友連8字都計錯<br />\n之後要求del post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就知好撚多神棍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實就算俾錢搵人算都唔知條友準唔準嫁<br />\n講D好多年後既事冇人保證到<br />\n但係到時你都追究唔到條友啦<br />\n話唔定過一兩年支那開拖打WW3 我地已經全部死晒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我試過好多次免費搵人算同埋俾錢搵人算<br />\n之後我覺得D結果冇乜參考價值<br />\n如果嫌姻緣唔好不如自己拎錢去整容好過<br />\n點都好過益班連basic野都錯既神棍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且行外人好難睇得穿佢地講得岩唔岩, 因為冇相關知識<br />\n反而佢地圍內成日鬼打鬼, 同行如敵國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026365bf2328d5dcfa1b1e030f7c4355d1e42a74","tid":1746382,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d21af2b57c137d8fee68fdbca939a33173b47f9","tid":1746382,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"你淨係睇連登有條友連8字都計錯<br />\n之後要求del post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就知好撚多神棍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:17:04.000Z","msg":"你講緊邊位???"},{"pid":"4e3b78706571cbdc4a9c38fc9118ccb9ba2cda45","tid":1746382,"uid":28580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"小心有人教你轉運"},{"pid":"1fe6469a5d40e3b6be8b0e99224f7d798057aa0c","tid":1746382,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e3b78706571cbdc4a9c38fc9118ccb9ba2cda45","tid":1746382,"uid":28580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"小心有人教你轉運"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"性交轉運 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n種生基都不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773b5cd0bc0cf8b5b313527649fe8